item.title: Hope - Journal
item.description: This is accompanied with Hope This is to maintain a daily journal of the efforts. This is to be seen from bottom to top. To explain the jargons: cw: current weight gw: goal weight Ok, lets start. February 25, 2021 cw: 75.45 pulls: 0 I forgot to do the pullups! In terms of walk I did a good pace with 7kms in 1:09:00 hrs. No books on Audible, rather some Indie songs Spotify and did not even feel those 7kms.
